node.text:
Nasi Goreng Istimewa
This is just wow! I’m a friedrice lover and this surpass expectations! Fragrant tasty rice with sambal prawns, delicious satay and a sunny side up from @chatterboxsg ! Definitely gonna order again👍🏽
🔻
Apart from this, I’ve tried the other more ‘atas’ friedrice too.. the Fragrant Wok-fried Rice with Crab Meat and Fish Roe and as usual the folks @shisenhanten doesn’t disappoint and I must say, this is really on point! Yes, it might look simple, but it’s really the perfect friedrice! From its grainy texture to the slight popping of the roe and flavors of the sea really won be over!!👍🏽
Get all these now at 50% off @chatterboxsg
